":{},"text":"The Carl D. Perkins Career and Technical Education Act of 2006, referred to in subsec. (d)(2), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/210"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–210","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1963-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 1963","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/77/403"},"text":"77 Stat. 403","children":[],"tail":", as amended generally by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/270/s1/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–270, § 1(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2006-08-12"},"text":"Aug. 12, 2006","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/120/683"},"text":"120 Stat. 683","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 44 (§ 2301 et seq.) of Title 20, Education. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s2301"},"text":"section 2301 of Title 20","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
